{"tid":1512303,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［求幫fc］啱啱老母send咗張咁嘅圖俾我","createTime":"2019-08-27T23:43:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-27T23:58:11.000Z","uid":230165,"like":1,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"379e6f86f2600f028bc317687c2399999bb568bb","tid":1512303,"uid":230165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T23:43:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UMra7sG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUMra7sG.jpg&h=35c51bcb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n自從我成功說服我老母轉陣之後，佢已經做咗我係藍絲群嘅針，每日都send個群嘅笑話俾我睇，如題佢今日send咗以上呢張圖俾我。<br />\n<br />\n其他笑話如下：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VN9TkPH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVN9TkPH.jpg&h=2dd66c72&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/G6pj0PJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FG6pj0PJ.png&h=9f068126&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GWntT9L.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGWntT9L.png&h=bb69c9a0&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/28/074321_3784748fac2ce84ae33e80591ef6034e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F28%2F074321_3784748fac2ce84ae33e80591ef6034e.png&h=c6b08ad8&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/28/074323_9ebab7764f5120674698f1c827c3ab4b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F28%2F074323_9ebab7764f5120674698f1c827c3ab4b.png&h=f1d1a39d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n原來警察部一直忍一直唔打幕後有一個天大原因 而中央下令不可用武力是有原因<br />\n因為目前中國香港vs英美是打一塲經濟戰爭<br />\n因為英美以用數以萬億買重香港經濟期指大跌（10月份)如果10月份內真喺打暴動 香港期指便會大跌 美國佬便賺好多好多中國香港億錢走。因此中央已洞悉此陰謀<br />\n故此即使佔中如果破壞經濟 中央一定死都托住個股市唔比大跌 費事比美國佬得嘗所願<br />\n亦下令警察不可用武力<br />\n亦不清塲 處處也忍 我相信高層是知道這原因 <br />\n所以打後12日班暴徒只會越玩越激 甚至會用武器來攻擊我們 所以要忍耐 一到11月期指結算完<br />\n無暴動無大跌 美國佬便會輸到仆街，便會逆轉乾抣 絕對用武力清塲<br />\n而家呢班友原来係英美用🇺🇸🇬🇧錢收買嘅打手, 走狗、漢奸！<br />\n這個一定係事情真相<br />\n要廣傳，救救無知学生"},{"pid":"dccc1847330c69f21f7a69767e8aa1c95fca7a9d","tid":1512303,"uid":230165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T23:44:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"16713464b87a7f8903a13c0e1ddc3a08e0490687","tid":1512303,"uid":230165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T23:44:29.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"cf6617fdc3fa9dac8ae6527a0c8897f61a597c36","tid":1512303,"uid":230165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T23:44:53.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"d5264971d75b22160c4c6e13e64302e78c0ec862","tid":1512303,"uid":230165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T23:45:09.000Z","msg":"再推"},{"pid":"bd64fb9c77bfd5e7deb5a22406f068e1e98ac18f","tid":1512303,"uid":230165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T23:45:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7eff06d753fc1a91a4f7ce49265e9de9ea9d70a4","tid":1512303,"uid":230165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T23:45:48.000Z","msg":"自推N下"},{"pid":"f63ba74625d3d19641ad51daac0a80eacb73ec88","tid":1512303,"uid":182088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T23:45:55.000Z","msg":"9up唔使本<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a12448f391070276789f398e4149b0e34f1e4949","tid":1512303,"uid":46966,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T23:45:57.000Z","msg":"第一句已經唔岩啦 又係作文<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca6014a021ff54b3bf129b4091645cfbb96a839b","tid":1512303,"uid":230165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T23:46:08.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"e8f0fc1dd53e6a66cf6c6504b8dbff923a22246f","tid":1512303,"uid":125079,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1